Parse growth data

# customise duration calculation
growth_data <- parse_growth(file = list.files(str_c(raw_dir, "/Growth_curves"), full.names = T, recursive = T),
                            duration = c(20, 10),
                            interval = 10,
                            n_skip = 12,
                            well_cols = "merged",
                            multiple_tranformations = c(1,1),
                            exp = experiment,
                            plate = str_remove(plate, "plate"),
                            normalised = F,
                            annotate = "none"
) %>%
 annotate_wells(well_info = "plate_info/well_info/well_info_plateGP8.csv", annotation = "none") 
## Parsing growth data from file Raw_data/plateGP8/exp210328//Growth_curves/210328 Plate GP8 n4 ON growth.xlsx

# save growth data
growth_data %>%
  write_csv(str_c(parse_dir, "growth_data_", plate, "_", experiment, ".csv"))
